# I have successfully moved to the position of the nearest iron ore resource.
#
# Now, I will attempt to harvest some iron ore to gather the necessary materials for smelting into iron plates.

# Attempting to harvest 10 iron ore from the resource.
harvested_quantity_iron = harvest_resource(position=nearest_iron_resource_position, quantity=10)  # Harvesting iron ore.

# Check how much iron ore was harvested.
print(f"Harvested Quantity of Iron Ore: {harvested_quantity_iron}")  # Output the amount of iron ore harvested.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check inventory after harvesting.
